Practical advice for new and progressing divers, grounded in real training.
As we work toward the PADI Divemaster rating, Tips shares what we're learning —
skills, safety, buoyancy, planning, and the habits that make you a better,
safer diver.

Everything here is built on responsible diving practice first.
